1
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,320
Young Master Xie, I hope you have been well.

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:14,080
You truly come and go without a sound, sir.

3
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,330
You didn't seek me out today

4
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,720
just to catch up, did you?

5
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,640
You are perceptive, sir.

6
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,720
Although I cannot see,

7
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,200
my heart is not blind.

8
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,480
Prince Ling was defeated in the past

9
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:30,080
because he didn't have Mr. Jin's full support.

10
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,880
Notify the Black Armor Guards.

11
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,440
In three days at midnight,

12
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,320
we strike.

13
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:39,200
Prince Ling plans to act in three days.

14
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,759
Start a rebellion.

15
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,930
I want to revive the Xie family.

16
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:52,720
I came specifically to ask Mr. Jin to come out of retirement

17
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,840
and advise me.

18
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,490
What do you have to offer me?

19
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,240
If I gain power in the future,

20
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,039
I will share half of all my gold and treasures

21
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,440
with you.

22
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,800
How generous.

23
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,480
What if I want

24
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,720
more than that?

25
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:11,200
What else do you want, Mr. Jin?

26
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,760
I have already fallen into the dust.

27
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,960
If Mr. Jin

28
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,480
wants anything,

29
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,770
feel free to take it.

30
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,000
I won't hold back.

31
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,450
Alright.

32
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,360
In that case,

33
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,800
from now on,

34
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,240
you'll call me Sir.

35
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,960
I am not your servant.

36
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,280
I am not your subject.

37
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,960
We are just cooperating.

38
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:41,720
Alright.

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,280
Sir.

40
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,220
If you want to revive your family,

41
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:50,320
the first step is not to form cliques,

42
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,180
nor to seek personal gain,

43
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,800
but to get married.

44
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,560
Sir.

45
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,250
What do you mean?

46
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,130
Marry into the Duke's mansion,

47
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,600
and wed Yan Mingli.

48
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:07,400
She probably hates me to the bone.

49
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,680
This way won't work.

50
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,420
Then you should resolve the hatred in her heart,

51
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,960
and breed love.

52
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,610
Madam Zhou is severely ill and bedridden.

53
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:22,240
Now is the best time for you

54
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,360
to move into the Duke's mansion.

55
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,600
May I ask you, sir,

56
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,560
what should I do?

57
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,640
From this moment on,

58
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,930
Xie Yuheng no longer exists in this world.

59
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:45,140
Tomorrow is the wedding of Heir Xiao and Princess Ling.

60
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,890
I should prepare some gifts

61
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,700
to add to the festivities.

62
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,360
Miss.

63
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:19,959
There are two distinguished guests from the Southern Border asking to see you.

64
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,760
The Southern Border?

65
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,660
Be careful, Young Master.

66
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,080
Who are you two?

67
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,240
I am Su Yan.

68
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,480
This is my master, Mr. Jin.

69
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,520
Greetings, Second Miss.

70
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,160
Greetings, Second Miss.

71
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,720
We are traveling from the Southern Border.

72
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:07,080
My young master has suffered from an eye disease since childhood.

73
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,960
I have long heard of the superb medical skills in Dafeng,

74
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,200
and came specifically to seek treatment.

75
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:12,200
I heard there is a good doctor in the Duke's estate,

76
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,120
so I took the liberty to intrude.

77
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:17,200
There is no one skilled in medicine in this estate.

78
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,960
Please leave.

79
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,520
What a pity.

80
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,440
Though I cannot see the scenery,

81
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,970
I smell the elegant fragrance of flowers.

82
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:31,360
The layout of the pavilions must be very elegant.

83
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,450
To manage affairs here,

84
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:36,580
the Second Young Lady must be an elegant person.

85
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,360
How do you know the layout of the pavilions?

86
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:42,640
The distance of footsteps, the wind blowing through gaps,

87
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,770
the pitch of echoes,

88
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,080
and even the strength of the floral scent.

89
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,940
A blind person's sense of hearing

90
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:52,690
sometimes perceives the subtle charm of a space better than a sighted person.

91
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,320
I once knew someone.

92
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,170
Though his eyes were clear,

93
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,450
his heart was as blind as the night.

94
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,920
Later, he lost his sight,

95
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,040
and cast me aside like an old shoe,

96
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,160
hurting me deeply.

97
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,660
Young Master Su, you actually

98
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,640
resemble him a bit.

99
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,680
It is that old acquaintance who lacks the fortune

100
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,520
and does not deserve the Second Young Lady's true heart.

101
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,760
If I could meet

102
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:25,560
someone as pure and kind as the Second Young Lady,

103
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,700
I would stay by her side for a lifetime

104
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,200
and never let her down.

105
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,120
"A pure and kind person."

106
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:35,920
From where did Young Master Su discern

107
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,360
my nature?

108
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,850
If the Second Young Lady

109
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,560
had no kind thoughts,

110
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,760
as soon as we stated our purpose,

111
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,730
you could have ordered your men to kick us out.

112
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:50,880
But not only did you allow me to prattle on in the estate for so long,

113
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:53,080
you were even willing to listen to a blind man like me

114
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:56,080
talk nonsense about pavilions and scenery.

115
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,960
What's more,

116
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:02,200
the Second Young Lady was willing to reveal some of her private thoughts

117
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,440
to a stranger.

118
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:07,020
How else to describe such a clear and unguarded nature,

119
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,800
if not pure

120
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,800
and kind?

121
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,400
This man is gentle as jade.

122
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:19,500
His speech and bearing are completely different from Xie Yuheng.

123
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,800
Perhaps I'm overthinking.

124
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,040
Young Master.

125
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:32,120
Since the Duke's estate doesn't have the good doctor we heard of,

126
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:35,090
let's not bother the Second Young Lady here anymore.

127
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,490
The journey was tiring.

128
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,890
We should find an inn to settle down early.

129
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,980
Second Young Lady,

130
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,200
farewell.

131
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,560
Please wait, you two.

132
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:52,240
There are still spare guest rooms in the manor.

133
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:55,010
You have traveled a long way and must be tired.

134
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:58,120
An inn is not as comfortable as the Duke's estate.

135
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,720
Xiaoyue,

136
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,800
take them to rest.

137
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:03,930
In that case,

138
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,370
we will impose on you, Second Miss.

139
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,420
We will take our leave.

140
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:16,740
It's not too late to leave after your eyes are cured.

141
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,410
Thank you, Second Miss.

142
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,160
This way, please.

143
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,520
Greetings, Mother Consort.

144
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,450
Mother Consort.

145
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:58,320
This place is cold and damp, which is not good for your health.

146
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,490
Liufang Palace has been prepared.

147
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,280
You should move back.

148
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,880
The Cold Palace is quiet.

149
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,250
The outside world is full of troubles.

150
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,680
You are my biological mother,

151
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,160
the noble Dowager Consort.

152
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,320
If anyone dares to gossip,

153
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,380
I will punish them.

154
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,820
You can punish gossip,

155
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,420
but can you control people's hearts?

156
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,320
Your Majesty is the ruler of a nation.

157
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,640
Sitting on this dragon throne,

158
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:30,170
you must be worthy of the vast lands of Dafeng,

159
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,440
the foundation laid by your ancestors,

160
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,200
and most importantly, the late Emperor's expectations

161
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,520
when he entrusted this empire to you.

162
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,840
What I have said,

163
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,080
do you understand, Emperor?

164
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,000
Your teachings are correct, Mother.

165
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,160
I know what to do.

166
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,400
There are still state affairs to attend to.

167
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,600
I shall take my leave.

168
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,760
Regarding the matter of moving back to Liufang Palace,

169
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,360
Mother, please reconsider.

170
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,840
My lord.

171
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,240
Prince Ling's wedding procession has reached the official road on the outskirts of the capital.

172
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:38,640
The bridal sedan chair is heading towards East Chang Street.

173
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,490
Saddle my horse.

174
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:46,080
One flower.

175
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,440
Two flowers.

176
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:51,680
Our princess is inside.

177
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,760
One mountain.

178
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,080
Two mountains.

179
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,290
Do you really not blame me, Mother,

180
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:03,460
for insisting on marrying the man who killed my father?

181
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,400
The grievances of the older generation

182
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:14,800
have already been buried with your father.

183
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,760
If you don't live your life well,

184
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,520
then I will truly blame you.

185
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,700
I understand your feelings for Prince Xiao.

186
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,200
Growing up,

187
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:28,320
you've never cared so much

188
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,760
about anyone or anything.

189
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,680
Except him.

190
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:34,080
I only hope you can stay with the one you love,

191
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,140
grow old together,

192
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,660
and be of one heart for a lifetime.

193
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,800
Father always loved me the most.

194
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,120
For what I am doing today,

195
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,300
I hope Father will forgive me.

196
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,600
One mountain.

197
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,800
Two mountains.

198
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,920
Our princess!

199
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:55,760
Run!

200
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,560
Run!

201
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,920
Prince Ling, that old thief, killed the envoys of Beidi.

202
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:15,120
Today, we will take his daughter's life

203
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,440
to honor the fallen heroes of Beidi.

204
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,640
Kill her!

205
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,530
Are you okay?

206
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,690
Come with me.

207
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,320
Cuimei.

208
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,160
Yong.

209
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:40,850
Weikun Huachao.

210
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,000
Longcong Biaohao.

211
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,580
Shuang Bin.

212
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:48,560
Ning Zheng.

213
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,220
Ning Zheng.

214
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:53,080
Haochun Kangshuaihua.

215
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:56,850
Wei Chao.

216
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:00,280
Qiangyuan Liangbo.

217
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:15,760
Xi.

218
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,040
Xi.

219
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,160
Taoqiang Xi.

220
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:18,880
Tao Qiang.

221
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,160
Huiyue Yunqing.

222
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,360
Yiyi.
